@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Identity
@using LeafLoop.Models
@inject SignInManager<User> SignInManager
@inject UserManager<User> UserManager

<ul class="navbar-nav">
    @if (SignInManager.IsSignedIn(User))
    {
        <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link" asp-controller="Profile" asp-action="Index" title="ZarzÄ…dzaj swoim profilem">
                <i class="bi bi-person-circle me-1"></i> @UserManager.GetUserAsync(User).Result?.FirstName
            </a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
            <form class="form-inline" asp-controller="Account" asp-action="Logout" method="post">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-link nav-link">
                    <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-right me-1"></i> Wyloguj
                </button>
            </form>
        </li>
    }
    else
    {
        <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link" asp-controller="Account" asp-action="Register">
                <i class="bi bi-person-plus me-1"></i> Rejestracja
            </a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link" asp-controller="Account" asp-action="Login">
                <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-in-right me-1"></i> Logowanie
            </a>
        </li>
    }
</ul>